  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Doton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> *</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 18 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 6 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You send your Chakra through the ground to cause up to one rock per 3 levels within range to explode. The Cost and effects of this technique depend on the size of the rocks targeted. You must may the Cost for each rock or boulder you target.<br><br>- Small (2 Chakra): 5 ft Burst, 1d6 earth damage.<br>- Medium (4 Chakra): 10 ft Burst, 2d8 earth damage.<br>- Large (6 Chakra): 20 ft Burst, 3d10 earth damage.<br>- Huge (8 Chakra): 30 ft Burst, 4d12 earth damage.<br><br>The area is centered on the targeted rock(s), and creatures within the area(s) can make a Reflex save to halve the damage. You can target a stone object you created with Shouchite or Kaigeki Chite no Jutsu. Such objects count as Large boulders, and are destroyed after exploding.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
